        }).setOrigin(0.5);
        this.physics.add.staticImage(ROOM_IDS.R3.start + 820, 1148, 'doorFrame')
            .setTint(BRANCH_CONFIG.A.color)
            .refreshBody();
```
That Y value (`1148`) aligns the door with the ground tiles so when you arrive in `R3` from `R2`, the door appears embedded in the floor and the player no longer “falls down from a floating door.”
